"Summer Sun Celebration
official overseer's checklist.

168
00:07:24,530 --> 00:07:25,320
"Number 1 --

169
00:07:25,450 --> 00:07:28,620
Banquet preparations,
Sweet Apple Acres."

170
00:07:29,290 --> 00:07:31,090
Yee-Haw!

171
00:07:37,660 --> 00:07:39,610
Let's get this over with.

172
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,270
Good afternoon.

173
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:43,410
My name
is Twilight Sparkle.

174
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,800
Well, Howdy-Do, ms. Twilight?

175
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:47,590
A pleasure making
your acquaintance.

176
00:07:47,890 --> 00:07:48,700
I'm Applejack.

177
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,370
We here
at Sweet Apple Acres

178
00:07:50,420 --> 00:07:51,850
