Apple Fritter.

192
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,930
Apple Bumpkin.

193
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,310
Red Gala.

194
00:08:32,570 --> 00:08:33,860
Red Delicious.
Golden Delicious.

195
00:08:33,970 --> 00:08:35,140
Caramel Apple.
Apple Strudel.

196
00:08:35,170 --> 00:08:36,240
Apple Tart.
Baked Apples.

197
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,690
Apple Brioche.
Apple Cinnamon Crisp.

198
00:08:38,710 --> 00:08:39,690
Big Macintosh.

199
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:43,980
Apple Bloom.
And...Granny Smith.

200
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:45,710
Up and at 'em,
Granny Smith.

201
00:08:45,780 --> 00:08:47,060
We got guests.

202
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,740
What?

203
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:49,960
Soup's on?

204
00:08:50,060 --> 00:08:52,230
I'm, uh, I'm coming,
I'm coming.

205
