keeping the sky clear.

230
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,490
I'm Twilight Sparkle,

231
00:10:36,530 --> 00:10:38,370
And the princess sent me
to check on the weather.

232
00:10:38,590 --> 00:10:40,350
Yeah, yeah.
That'll be a snap.

233
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:41,620
I'll do it in a jiffy,

234
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:43,490
